# Simple Arithmetic Calculator in C

## Description
This program performs the five basic arithmetic operations on two integers entered by the user.

## Concepts Used
- Variables
- Input and Output
- Arithmetic Operators
- Type Casting
- Modulus Operator

## Sample Output

Enter x = 20
Enter y = 6

Sum = 26
Difference = 14
Product = 120
Quotient = 3.33
Remainder = 2

